Pre-built libdatachannel static library will be placed here.

To build it yourself:
1. Ensure OpenSSL is installed on your system
2. Run: cd thirdparty && cmake -B build -S . -G "Visual Studio 17 2022" -A x64
3. Run: cmake --build build --config RelWithDebInfo --target datachannel-static
4. Copy: build/libdatachannel/RelWithDebInfo/datachannel-static.lib to this location as datachannel.lib

File size: ~20-30 MB (static library with all dependencies)
